The '''notice board''' is a notice board which displays tasks players may do on [[Fossil Island]]. Different sets of tasks will grant different rewards from [[Peter]], who can be found panning just west of the [[Museum Camp]]. Each set of tasks will reward 5 [[unidentified fossil]]s of the same type, which means doing these tasks will provide an opportunity to fill one [[Paleontology]] exhibit in the [[Varrock Museum]].

==Island tasks==
===Museum Camp===
After completing this list, players can receive 5 [[unidentified small fossil]]s by speaking to [[Peter]]. The items needed in total are 25 nails, 10 oak planks, 5 planks, 3 soft clay, 2 iron bars, 2 logs, 2 ropes, a bucket, as well as a hammer and a tinderbox. Nails do not bend on any of the objects.

